OL,3,CBusinesses say Stroud's Night Angels
OL,4,Care 'invaluable'
OL,6,FA group of women who patrol the
OL,7,Fstreets at night to keep women safe
OL,8,Fare "invaluable", according to night-
OL,9,Ftime economy bosses.
OL,11,F, now made up of around fifty
OL,12,Fvolunteers, was set up by Chrissie
OL,13,FLowery in Stroud to coincide with the
OL,14,Fopening of a new nightclub, Trio, in
OL,15,Fthe town.
OL,17,FEvery Friday and Saturday night
OL,18,Fbetween 11pm and 4am, a team of six
OL,19,Fwomen wearing pink high-viz jackets
OL,20,Fpatrol the streets of Stroud
OL,21,Fresponding to incidents in the town.
