OL,3,CBusinesses say Stroud's Night Angels
OL,4,Care 'invaluable'
OL,6,FMs Lowery, following a series of
OL,7,Fsexual assaults in the area, said the
OL,8,FNight Angels is the latest step in
OL,9,Fhelping women feel safe.
OL,11,FShe said: "I know a lot of women who
OL,12,Fhave said to me they won't even walk
OL,13,Ftheir dogs now, they won't go jogging,
OL,14,Fand now people can feel more safe to
OL,15,Fcome out and enjoy their nighttimes."
OL,17,FThe volunteers have dealt with 58
OL,18,Fincidents in the town since the
OL,19,Fproject began in December 2023.
