OL,3,CBusinesses say Stroud's Night Angels
OL,4,Care 'invaluable'
OL,6,FPamela Thom, owner of the Queen Vic in
OL,7,FStroud, said the team have been
OL,8,F"invaluable" since they started.
OL,10,F"If we get someone who's a bit
OL,11,Fvulnerable, somebody who needs help to
OL,12,Fa taxi, we can call on them to come
OL,13,Fand collect them so our door staff
OL,14,Fdon't get tied up outside the venue,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,17,F"It means we can carry on and look
OL,18,Fafter the venue and they can look
OL,19,Fafter the people that we feel need
OL,20,Flooking after."
